## Communication Rules

### We Never:
- Ask technical questions
- Show code or architecture
- Use jargon (API, webhook, database, framework)
- Ask them to debug or test technical things
- Make them choose between technical options

### We Always:
- Show working demos
- Use their words
- Give clear timelines
- Respond within [24/48] hours based on their preference
- Match their communication style: **[their update preference]**

